					<div class="grid gap-6 my-16 lg:grid-cols-3">
						<div class="flex flex-col p-8 space-y-4 rounded-md bg-gray-900">
							<div class="flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 text-xl font-bold rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-gray-900">1</div>
							<p class="text-2xl">
								<b>Contact Us.</b> Come by or give us a call.  We'll set up a time to go flying
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col p-8 space-y-4 rounded-md bg-gray-900">
