							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col p-8 space-y-4 rounded-md bg-gray-900">
							<div class="flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 text-xl font-bold rounded-full bg-teal-500 text-gray-900">3</div>
							<p class="text-2xl">
								<b>Start Instructing.</b> Teach others the joy of flight.  Share your passion for aviation.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
